123 /* ================================================================================ */
124 /* Macro to modify desired bitfields of a register */
125 #define WR_REG(reg, mask, pos, val) reg = (((uint32_t)val << pos) & \
126  ((uint32_t)mask)) | \
127  (reg & ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)mask)))
128 
129 /* Macro to modify desired bitfields of a register */
130 #define WR_REG_SIZE(reg, mask, pos, val, size) { \
131 uint##size##_t VAL1 = (uint##size##_t)((uint##size##_t)val << pos); \
132 uint##size##_t VAL2 = (uint##size##_t) (VAL1 & (uint##size##_t)mask); \
133 uint##size##_t VAL3 = (uint##size##_t)~((uint##size##_t)mask); \
134 uint##size##_t VAL4 = (uint##size##_t) ((uint##size##_t)reg & VAL3); \
135 reg = (uint##size##_t) (VAL2 | VAL4);\
136 }
137 
139 #define RD_REG(reg, mask, pos) (((uint32_t)reg & (uint32_t)mask) >> pos)
140 
142 #define RD_REG_SIZE(reg, mask, pos,size) ((uint##size##_t)(((uint32_t)reg & \
143  (uint32_t)mask) >> pos) )
144 
146 #define SET_BIT(reg, pos) (reg |= ((uint32_t)1<<pos))
147 
149 #define CLR_BIT(reg, pos) (reg = reg & (uint32_t)(~((uint32_t)1<<pos)) )
